{"tid":1118103,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"諗左幾日, 其實「黑洞」關時間變慢咩事?","createTime":"2019-04-21T07:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T11:15:06.000Z","uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d59c0b21ec6690c4875b59fc3c1cda08fc6af4ff","tid":1118103,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"講得最多係黑洞個「事件視界」,<br />\n如果A 比黑洞吸左去事件視界, 再入奇點, <br />\n咁遙遠既觀察員B 就只會睇到A永遠停留事件視界。因為黑洞引力大過光, 所以A之後既事B 係睇唔到。<br />\n<br />\n咁關時間變慢咩事?<br />\n<br />\n係A 既角度, 佢時間無變, 一路衝緊入奇點; <br />\n係B 既角度, 佢時間都無變, 佢只係「視像」上見到B停左, 但雙方實際時間都係無變。<br />\n<br />\n即係好似YOUTUBE 直播咁, A 直播中, <br />\nB 睇睇下pause 左10分鐘再睇, 咁B慢左10分鐘, <br />\n但時間一樣無變慢, 只係影像停留左<br />\n<br />\n咁關時間變慢咩事?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50793a89afba6976175660de2b21cfa65d36b2c8","tid":1118103,"uid":35317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/引力時間膨脹\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%86%A8%E8%84%B9&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=d125ea86\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/引力時間膨脹</a>"},{"pid":"0a0e6c9e66936aadc5689f70b8b7f5ee3ea6e717","tid":1118103,"uid":248720,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34a63b50dd0a4e8c877f2b1b716e15a1355e5ae8","tid":1118103,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"相對論下話"},{"pid":"9c5ffede98f749f1efd2b65e265ac70bb37da848","tid":1118103,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"有無睇過相對論"},{"pid":"95fb72d8d9b0db150a8b288f9f3c07002a4c7d1b","tid":1118103,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-2